data.description: Your new home awaits you in this spacious four bedroom, three bathroom house with large outdoor entertainment space and an above ground pool. This home has plenty of space for your family to enjoy and a fully fenced in yard for your kids and pets to run and play. Large living space is open with kitchen and dining. Master suite has large bathroom and walk-in closet attached with plenty of storage. On the other side of the house, you’ll find three additional bedrooms. This one won’t last long! Call today to schedule your private showing.
